OL,4,CMorrisons rejects #5.5bn offer from US
OL,5,Cprivate equity firm
OL,6, Morrisons has rejected a #5.5bn
OL,7, takeover proposal from US private
OL,8, equity firm Clayton, Dubilier & Rice.
OL,10,FThe UK's fourth-largest supermarket,
OL,11,Fwith 118,000 staff, said the offer
OL,12,F"significantly undervalues" the firm.
OL,14,FCD&R, where former Tesco boss Sir Terry
OL,15,FLeahy is an advisor, confirmed it was
OL,16,Fconsidering a formal bid after weekend
OL,17,Fmedia speculation about its plans.
OL,19,FThe US firm has previously made
OL,20,Finvestments in the discount shop chain
OL,21,FB&M, from which it made more than #1bn.
